page.title: 01A DAY IN THE LIFE OF NANCY
page.content: I get up at 7:30 and go down to breakfast. For breakfast I have cereal called Corn Flakes. I have them with cold milk. I also have fresh orange juice. I go to school in a car with Mum and two girls. The school I go to is called Therfield. We go swimming in a town nearby called Buntingford every Tuesday.My best friend is Zoe. School starts at 9:15. Zoe and I check the rainfall gauge first then we have lessons: they are Maths.,English, Interest,Computer & Science. We have two types of Maths.,one is called Beta, the other is called Fletcher. I like Interest best, you learn about countries & animals & write about them.On Friday we have a special Maths. test. I like going on the computer as well:we have lots of computer games. I get home at 3:30 & watch television & play my recorder.
